\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13984732\charrsid3805323 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 ograph. No small watches as there is today and we thought they was something then when they had a watch and chain.
