\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 ip at one side and go in and walk - we could just walk across with water up - to our nec}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13984732\charrsid3805323 k}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323  and carry our clothes across to the other side for when the policeman came. He'd take our clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 What happened when he took your clothes - how did you get them back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 You had to go to their house for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 To the policeman's house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Officially you weren't supposed to be in the canal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 No, you wasn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Did your parents worry about you doing this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 You never let your parents know. You used to - rub dirt on your face, so as your parents wouldn't know you'd been in the canal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Did you ever know anyone get drowned though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Get drowned - let's see. I don't remember anyone being drowned swimming. I remember people being drowned at committing sui
cide. Not swimming and where - the - there's been a crowd on - on the canal bank and the police grappling, with a grappling iron and bringing them in and then putting them on a stretcher - there was no mortuary then. And they used to put 'em on a stretche
r and walk through the streets with 'em to - a stable at a public house. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 What would happen then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Well - they awaited the coroner. Hold an inquest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 And they would stay in there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 And they would hold an inquest and then they'd go where?
