\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Do you remember a funeral at all in the family and who attended - do you remember a funeral in those days and what it was like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Yes, well - I remember funerals 
but they used to walk to the churchyard in those days, because there wasn't - they couldn't afford coaches. And they used to walk and there used to be a lot of their friends and neighbours as used to go.
