\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Do you remember what kind of clothes they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Yes, they wore what they called their Sunday 
best. They used to wear what they could afford you see, they didn't get any special clothes for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Do you remember anything special about funerals at all when you were a child?
