\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 Well same as I tell you, me mother was there she punish you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 How did she punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 By the - yes.
