\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16685 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 The dinner or the breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10167806 FH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14758297\charrsid3805323 I had to take both. Yes, the dinner and all.
